NEXORA CONTENT ENGINE v3
========================

SYSTEM OVERVIEW
---------------
Self-improving content + performance intelligence system.
Generates viral scripts → tracks platform metrics → scores content → learns → adapts.

DAILY FLOW
----------
9:00 AM  →  python content_engine.py morning
             Generates Video 1 (Problem/Insight) + Video 2 (Demo/Conversion)
             Sends full scripts to Telegram (Word-ready format)

4:00 PM  →  python content_engine.py afternoon
             Sends check-in to team: posted? comments? WhatsApp leads?
             Team replies: posted=yes comments=X leads=X

9:00 PM  →  python content_engine.py evening [leads_count]
             Pulls Meta + TikTok metrics
             Scores each post (out of 100)
             Identifies top + weak post
             Generates AI insight + action for tomorrow
             Saves all data to Google Sheets
             Sends performance report to Telegram

SCORING SYSTEM (out of 100)
----------------------------
Reach Score        20 pts  →  views + reach vs baseline
Engagement Score   30 pts  →  likes, comments (x2), shares (x3), saves (x2)
Retention Proxy    20 pts  →  saves + shares as watch-completion signal
Conversion Score   30 pts  →  WhatsApp leads received

CLASSIFICATIONS
---------------
80–100  →  SCALE    (replicate aggressively)
60–79   →  OPTIMIZE (tweak hook or CTA)
40–59   →  WEAK     (rethink format)
<40     →  DROP     (kill the concept)

MODULES
-------
content/script_generator.py    →  Claude API → daily viral scripts
content/performance_tracker.py →  Meta Graph API + TikTok API metrics
content/content_scorer.py      →  Scores posts 0–100
content/learning_engine.py     →  Pattern analysis + AI insight
content/sheets_manager.py      →  Google Sheets history

